# Run your function locally with `func start host`
@baseUrl = http://localhost:7071/api
@threadId = <your-thread-id-without-double-quotes-or-single-quotes>

### 1) Start a new chat thread
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/newchat
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 2) Missing parameters for conversation (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversation
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 3) Valid conversation turn via POST
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversation HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "thread_id": "{{threadId}}",
    "question": "How are you doing today?"
}

### 4) Another conversation turn via POST
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversation HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "thread_id": "{{threadId}}",
    "question": "Adding new conversation history to Azure Cosmos DB."
}